00:25:46.155 --> 00:25:49.334
to die yet, he's in this coma, but his soul

554
00:25:49.334 --> 00:25:53.888
is requesting council. So I can go to him,

555
00:25:53.888 --> 00:25:56.693
I can bring his soul here to this healing place

