00:25:56.693 --> 00:25:59.904
and talk to him and say, "Let's look at your blueprint,

557
00:25:59.904 --> 00:26:02.250
"let's look at your plan. Here's what will happen

558
00:26:02.250 --> 00:26:04.799
"if you leave your body now, here's what will happen

559
00:26:04.799 --> 00:26:06.911
"if you stay in for another five years

560
00:26:06.911 --> 00:26:09.631
"or 10 years or whatever. If you leave now,

561
00:26:09.631 --> 00:26:12.319
"here is the myriad of lessons

562
00:26:12.319 --> 00:26:15.135
"that you will learn, your family members,

