00:26:20.308 --> 00:26:22.420
"So which would you like to choose?"

566
00:26:22.420 --> 00:26:26.323
Not only is that man's soul making that choice,

567
00:26:26.323 --> 00:26:28.574
but all the other members of his soul family.

568
00:26:28.574 --> 00:26:30.963
His wife who is sitting next to the bed crying,

569
00:26:30.963 --> 00:26:34.035
his children who are looking over his will,

570
00:26:34.035 --> 00:26:36.840
whoever's involved on a soul level,

571
00:26:36.840 --> 00:26:39.005
even though they're not aware of it,

572
00:26:39.005 --> 00:26:41.277
all of those souls are convening and saying,

