00:26:48.103 --> 00:26:52.652
There all done by agreement, he showed me how that happens.

576
00:26:52.652 --> 00:26:56.507
A person who is dying or in a coma

577
00:26:56.507 --> 00:27:01.082
can request healing assistance

578
00:27:01.082 --> 00:27:04.469
and be greeted by people like Danny

579
00:27:04.469 --> 00:27:06.539
and guides and angels of all kinds

580
00:27:06.539 --> 00:27:09.227
to sit and help them make that decision,

581
00:27:09.227 --> 00:27:10.763
but don't make it alone because

582
00:27:10.763 --> 00:27:13.430
the members of their soul family are affected as well.

583
00:27:13.430 --> 00:27:17.888
On that level, all those souls are in the mix.

584
00:27:19.838 --> 00:27:22.863
It's like pieces of a kaleidoscope.

585
00:27:22.863 --> 00:27:24.644
If you look at a kaleidoscope and it turns

586
00:27:24.644 --> 00:27:28.452
just a tiny little bit, all of the pieces restructure,

587
00:27:28.452 --> 00:27:31.310
and that's how every free will decision

