00:28:32.235 --> 00:28:35.824
moved the kaleidoscope one little niche,

608
00:28:35.824 --> 00:28:38.533
so everybody's your soul family.

609
00:28:38.533 --> 00:28:40.400
<v Regina>That broadens it out to the extent</v>

