00:28:40.400 --> 00:28:43.621
where it can be any experience that you wish.

611
00:28:43.621 --> 00:28:45.573
<v ->It's every experience, yeah.</v>

612
00:28:45.573 --> 00:28:47.781
<v Regina>Every experience in anywhere, in any shape.</v>

