00:29:14.531 --> 00:29:18.243
in that widening circle, agreed to be here

624
00:29:18.243 --> 00:29:20.845
at this moment for this experience, for each of them

625
00:29:20.845 --> 00:29:25.845
there was a requested growth lesson.

