00:29:38.100 --> 00:29:41.520
and you can be in "that man killed my child"

631
00:29:41.520 --> 00:29:44.210
and work with it that way, or you can be in,

632
00:29:44.210 --> 00:29:46.397
"maybe we all had an agreement to meet

633
00:29:46.397 --> 00:29:48.690
"here at this moment for this experience"

634
00:29:48.690 --> 00:29:50.621
and work with it that way.

635
00:29:50.621 --> 00:29:53.820
<v Regina>Yes. Now going to the work</v>

