00:33:06.391 --> 00:33:07.492
<v Regina>Yeah exactly.</v>

715
00:33:07.492 --> 00:33:08.381
(both laugh)

716
00:33:08.381 --> 00:33:10.237
<v ->But for some people it is because</v>

