00:33:45.346 --> 00:33:47.245
They have to lower their frequency.

735
00:33:47.245 --> 00:33:49.058
<v Regina>Exactly, and that's what she was</v>

736
00:33:49.058 --> 00:33:51.682
explaining to me and it's, "Oh, no problem

737
00:33:51.682 --> 00:33:53.474
"Mom! Go have fun!"

738
00:33:53.474 --> 00:33:55.095
<v ->How hard is it for you to raise your frequency?</v>

739
00:33:55.095 --> 00:33:56.006
<v Regina>Exactly, exactly.</v>

740
00:33:56.006 --> 00:33:57.021
<v ->And so you meet in the middle.</v>

